# Employee Attendance Management System вЂ” Implementation Plan

## Overview

A production-ready **Employee Attendance Management System** built with Flutter (frontend) + Firebase (backend). Supports Admin and Employee roles with punch-in/out tracking, attendance reporting (Excel export), and real-time Telegram notifications вЂ” all on **free-tier services**. State management uses **Provider**.

---

## 1. System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Flutter App"
        UI["Screens (Admin / Employee)"]
        RP["ChangeNotifier Providers"]
        SVC["Service Layer"]
        MDL["Models"]
    end

    subgraph "Firebase"
        FA["Firebase Auth"]
        FS["Cloud Firestore"]
        FCM["Firebase Cloud Messaging"]
    end

    subgraph "External"
        TG["Telegram Bot API"]
    end

    UI --> RP --> SVC
    SVC --> FA
    SVC --> FS
    SVC --> FCM
    SVC --> TG
    MDL -.-> SVC
```

| Layer | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| **Screens** | Flutter widgets вЂ” forms, dashboards, lists |
| **Provider (ChangeNotifiers)** | State management, async data, caching |
| **Service Layer** | Abstracts Firebase SDK + HTTP calls (Telegram) |
| **Models** | Dart data classes with `fromJson` / `toJson` |
| **Firebase** | Auth, Firestore database, push notifications |
| **Telegram Bot API** | Free push notifications via HTTP POST |

---

## 2. Firestore Data Structure

### Collection: `users`

```
users/{uid}
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ name: string
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ email: string
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ phone: string
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ employeeId: string          // e.g. "EMP-001"
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ department: string
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ role: string                // "admin" | "employee"
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ createdAt: timestamp
в””в”Ђв”Ђ updatedAt: timestamp
```

### Collection: `attendance`

```
attendance/{autoId}
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ uid: string                 // FK в†’ users/{uid}
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ employeeId: string          // denormalized for queries
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ employeeName: string        // denormalized for display
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ date: string                // "2026-02-23" вЂ” partition key
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ punchIn: timestamp | null
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ punchOut: timestamp | null
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ totalHours: double | null
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ status: string              // "present" | "absent" | "late"
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ createdAt: timestamp
в””в”Ђв”Ђ updatedAt: timestamp
```

> **Compound index**: `(date ASC, uid ASC)` for the admin daily dashboard.

### Collection: `settings`

```
settings/app
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ lateThresholdMinutes: int   // e.g. 15 (punch-in later than 09:15 в†’ late)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ workStartTime: string       // "09:00"
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ telegramBotToken: string
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ telegramChatId: string
```

