## 7. Excel Export Implementation

### Package: `syncfusion_flutter_xlsio`

```dart
// Pseudocode
final Workbook workbook = Workbook();
final Worksheet sheet = workbook.worksheets[0];

// Headers
sheet.getRangeByIndex(1, 1).setText('Employee ID');
sheet.getRangeByIndex(1, 2).setText('Name');
sheet.getRangeByIndex(1, 3).setText('Date');
sheet.getRangeByIndex(1, 4).setText('Punch In');
sheet.getRangeByIndex(1, 5).setText('Punch Out');
sheet.getRangeByIndex(1, 6).setText('Total Hours');
sheet.getRangeByIndex(1, 7).setText('Status');

// Populate rows from List<AttendanceModel> ...

final List<int> bytes = workbook.saveAsStream();
workbook.dispose();

// Save to device
final directory = await getApplicationDocumentsDirectory();
final file = File('${directory.path}/attendance_report.xlsx');
await file.writeAsBytes(bytes);

// Share or open
await OpenFilex.open(file.path);
```

**Filters supported**: date range picker (`showDateRangePicker`) + employee dropdown в†’ Firestore compound query в†’ export matching docs.

