## 12. API Flow Diagrams

### Punch-In Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Employee
    participant App as Flutter App
    participant FS as Firestore
    participant TG as Telegram Bot

    E->>App: Tap "Punch In"
    App->>FS: Query attendance (date=today, uid=me)
    FS-->>App: [] (no record)
    App->>App: Calculate status (present/late)
    App->>FS: Create attendance doc
    FS-->>App: Success
    App->>TG: POST /sendMessage (punch-in notification)
    TG-->>App: 200 OK
    App->>E: Show "Punched In at 09:02 AM"
```

### Admin Export Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Admin
    participant App as Flutter App
    participant FS as Firestore

    A->>App: Select date range + employee filter
    App->>FS: Query attendance (date range, optional uid)
    FS-->>App: List<AttendanceModel>
    App->>App: Generate Excel workbook
    App->>App: Save to device storage
    App->>A: Open / Share .xlsx file
```

